Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Higurashi Real Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Behind this modest company name,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿is something really fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We've been thinking of moving lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So we wanted to see if there are any vacant condo spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry if it's a bit sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Somebody told us that we'd be able to find one quicker here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Actually, we're about to get married soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, congratulations to you two then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do you have any preferences about the place or about the rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're thinking of renting a spacious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A spacious one, right? I'll see if there are any immediate vacancies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This one has two floors and is 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's old, but it's a lot cheaper than the one beside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This one is new and has three rooms for living dining and kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's also on the top floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you two have opposing views.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How about taking something in the middle? Like this perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't want an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It has to be at least a condo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tthis one is three years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's quite close to the station, at the top floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿with three spacious rooms for dining, living, and a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's a bit over your budget,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿but the kitchen provides the latest electrical appliances and equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The security here is very good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san, you love it here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wait, I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Let's try looking for other vacancies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't you already feel like choosing this one after having seen it only once?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.77,0:01:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But it's quite over our budget, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just start working again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But this would hurt us financially.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll just make you packed lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's close to the station, but it's pretty far from where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Besides, this will be our first time living together as a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well... you're right.
