Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So, the two newlyweds chose that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But, I'm a bit worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿About the rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Or about their relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Both, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Their viewpoints are totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And their total income doesn't seem to be that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The husband seems to be working at a pretty standard firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So his income is enough, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He is a bit of a cheapskate though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The wife on the other hand, even though she has worked part-time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿never really acquired any experience working full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I don't think you should judge our customers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Circumstances did allow them to become engaged, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sayako-san, you're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes, partly because I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dinner's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is such a joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, Sayako-san can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You have to wake up early, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, you're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, just once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿{\3c&HCE4D9A&}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We haven't done it for three weeks already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Jeez, I'm not in the mood for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We've only done it three times since we started living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You were keeping count?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Idiot! I'm not going to wake you up tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You never did anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're always asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sayako-san, l wonder when she'll start working.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sex services, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've never been inside one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No one's inviting me to drink anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Asleep again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's dinner is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What should I eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Though, I really don't have money, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The regular beef bowl and miso soup, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, it's the real estate agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Morita-san! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This place is near my workplace so I came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You look a lot more stressed than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Actually, I'm thinking of filing for a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sayako-san didn't cook again, and she even said she'd love to use that kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She also doesn't do her part of the chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And it looks like she has no plans of ever finding a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's the exact opposite of what she said before we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I felt like my age was catching up with me, so I rushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sayako-san is actually quite older than me,\N﻿so I thought she'd be more dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I thought it'd be like having free sex,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿but she doesn't even let me have that, this is just too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've heard that Morita-san's wife is actually older than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But, she's quite gorgeous, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I heard she never goes to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿and with Morita-san slowly driven towards sex services,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿it'll be just a matter of time before that condo falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine with just them paying the rent regularly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But they're bound to get divorced if this goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How about I go get the pay for the rent this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is Higurashi Real Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Morita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We have come to collect the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Huh? Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm going to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then Miss, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Okay, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A delivery man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'﻿m sorry, were you entertaining another guest earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, it's alright. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, give me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Eh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have it. Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm sorry, the guy must have forgotten this earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a jiffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't you find that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The way she acts,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿and do delivery men usually forget their packages?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Of course they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're clearly committing adultery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm sure they were at it like this until we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Right here, in this very place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She'll be coming back very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Then we just have to do it fast as well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Move more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Faster, do it faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, if Morita-san's wife was really cheating,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿then it's definitely headed towards divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Normally it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, it's just that we were actually talking about you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Actually, she got pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We weren't having sex that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿but I guess if a chance presents itself, it can really come, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Even if it is her child, the baby is still our seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well then, I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, it's Morita-san's child... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry you had to come in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, I think we should really consider accepting bank payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You seem to be capable of doing lots of work on your own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Minorikawa-kun, do you want to try working as the company's boss like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm about to quit the job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, can you look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a list enumerating all our customers and clients
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who want payments to be made via bank deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So you did all this, huh? Why don't you try it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I already said I'm about to quit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss... are you really serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is there anything that would bother you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is there anything that you still don't understand about the necessary paperwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You see, it may not seem like it, but I actually trust you deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Was boss really serious about quitting the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll be leaving all the rents that I've been handling to you from now on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Soon-to-be Mr.President.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that... It just got me all worried now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Excuse me, this is Higurashi Real Estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh yes, who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I came to receive the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh? It's not Ms. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Did Ms. President have a headache or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Have you known her for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes, she has been taking care of me ever since I moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Getting the rent once a month, and visiting the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She always gets to be the one I talk with, how sweet of her really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Indeed she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why are you the one getting it and not Ms. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, boss is quite busy at the moment, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And I just got some juicy info for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Were you able to make you debut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I passed the first screening for the top 500
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿in HB company's sci-fi short story awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is that good or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ms. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ms. President, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He just ran away, and now I don't have anywhere else to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, but I'm no longer the President here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, then who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Him, Minorikawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿President!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Minorikawa-kun, no Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Please, I can settle for anything cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But, I just can't suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I can also stay at your place... If you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Of course, I'll do my best at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿President Minorikawa, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm going to find a place that you can rent right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So just wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I said I'm okay with your place, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, I'm definitely going to find one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, what a busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll sort the papers so that we can write out the necessary documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You can go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Okay, starting tomorrow, you're now in charge of everything in this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do your best, President Minorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, renting a place, can actually be quite hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are you suddenly saying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're actually employed and working, and\N﻿yet there's no one to see you through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Your income might not be enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿you might get too old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You might get rejected for various other reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿After coming to this place, I realized something new that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's why, please don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Now I can retire in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss, I still want to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Minorikawa-kun, weren't you irritated by it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You thought that I was some pervert, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well, yeah I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm actually... kind of glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The words that you just spoke earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿let me see just how sincere you really were when you uttered them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is the office, if someone comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Just thinking about it makes you feel excited, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,B-﻿Boss...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's it, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's going deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It really feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Cum inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Minorikawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Minorikawa-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿{\3c&HCE4D9A&}Boss, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I wonder how many times this has happened now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there are big offices here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's hard for even the locals to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why don't we just visit that last and final office that they referred us to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿﻿Excuse me, is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Minorikawa-kun, introduce it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sure, boss!